keyFacts: The document is a hardware serial/label record for a Western Digital Gold SATA hard drive, model WD2005FBYZ.
The drive has a capacity of 2.0TB and a serial number WMCSN0F1TWPA.
The date on the label is December 30, 2016.
The drive is noted as a product of Malaysia, with warranty information referencing Noorddorp, Netherlands.
The document contains no narrative text, names of individuals, or explicit references to events, locations, or entities related to the Epstein case.
